{"tid":306628,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮公布川普團隊薪資　核心幕僚年薪140萬","createTime":"2017-07-02T16:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T17:06:23.000Z","uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79aa256003cdf9be016032a558d329eb1b1978d2","tid":306628,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170701/640_d21f37482ff52d219481f402cd767509.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170701%2F640_d21f37482ff52d219481f402cd767509.jpg&h=4bd1abb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國白宮6月30日公布川普幕僚薪資單，長達16頁的文件，詳列近400名白宮人員薪資。<br />\n其中西翼核心幕僚，包括白宮幕僚長蒲博斯（Reince Priebus）、白宮首席策士班農（Steve Bannon）、白宮發言人史派瑟（Sean Spicer）、白宮高級顧問康薇（Kellyanne Conway）和白宮社群媒體總監史卡維諾（Dan Scavino Jr.）等年薪每人為17萬9千7百美元（約台幣550萬）。白宮副發言人珊德斯（Sarah Sanders）年薪為16萬5千美元（約台幣505萬）。<br />\n另外，擔任川普顧問的女兒伊凡卡和女婿庫西納則是不支薪。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.whitehouse.gov/sites/whitehouse.gov/files/docs/disclosures/07012017-report-final.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fsites%2Fwhitehouse.gov%2Ffiles%2Fdocs%2Fdisclosures%2F07012017-report-final.pdf&d=aVcppPIl750UK%2B5g1D2hLwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=f8e5ea0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.whitehouse.gov/sites/whitehouse.gov/files/docs/disclosures/07012017-report-final.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報 - 台灣"},{"pid":"3dcba8ac3fe9741a7656ab89d745e92c2bd525cf","tid":306628,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:06:23.000Z","msg":"1"}]}